attributes.action: Impose Financial Sanctions Against The UAE
attributes.additional_details: I want the UK government to do it because the people of Sudan deserve to have their lives back. I think that the UK, as a member of the G7 and the UN security council, has the power, influence and leverage to help end this conflict once and for all. An end to this conflict would save lives and peace could return to one of the largest countries in Africa.
attributes.background: There have been a number of reports that the UAE is supporting the Rapid Support Forces in Sudan. I would like for the UK government to impose sanctions against the UAE because of this. I hope these sanctions could help allow peace to reign in the region.
